Package: adastrumm
Title: Fit an Adaptively-Structured Mixed Model to Simple Clustered Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Helen", "Ogden", email = "heogden12@gmail.com",
                       role = c("aut", "cre"),
                       comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7204-9776"))
Description: Implements adaptively-structured mixed models for simple
    clustered data. These models estimate a flexible population mean
    function and learn a low-dimensional random-effects structure from the
    data, allowing individual trajectories and population-level variation to
    be estimated without pre-specifying the form of the random effects.
